        com.fiorano.edbc.framework.service.configuration.ConnectionlessServiceConfiguration

PropertyModel class captures the configuration information from the Custom Property Sheet (CPS) of the component. set methods set the property to the values provided in CPS and get methods can be used to get those values. JMX Naming conventions should be followed for these method names.
